  <T n="entry_text">0x96B57121<!--String: "Gibbi Point Locals"--></T>
  <V n="entry_text_description" t="enabled">
    <T n="enabled">0x17D05852<!--String: "Gibbi Point is known as an overly hospitable world, and the locals here generally try to be hospitable themselves (with a few exceptions!). You'll find they're full of opinions about one another and about some elements of life here, from the Peculiar Plumbird to some of Gibbi Point's older landmarks. You might want to try seeing if some of the locals will tell you more about themselves. Interested in becoming an honorary local yourself? Try cooking and eating some Jellyfish Salad and see how you feel afterward. "--></T>
  </V>
